ACADEMIC USE NOTICE:

This project was developed as part of the Boston University Online Master of 
Data Science (OMDS) program, Module C Capstone (DX 799S O2), under the 
instruction of Professor Joshua Von Korff.

DATASETS USED:

1. UNSW-NB15 Dataset
   - Source: UNSW Canberra Cyber Range Lab
   - Citation: Moustafa, N., & Slay, J. (2015). UNSW-NB15: A comprehensive 
     data set for network intrusion detection systems. Military Communications 
     and Information Systems Conference (MilCIS).
   - License: Available for academic research purposes

2. BETH Dataset
   - Source: Kaggle (katehighnam/beth-dataset)
   - Citation: Highnam, K., et al. (2021). BETH Dataset: Real-World Honeypot 
     Telemetry for Cybersecurity Research.
   - License: Check dataset page for current terms

